{"type": "article", "id": 58018, "title": "包包总是一团乱？这款科技配件收纳包来帮你｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-05T22:52:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53984, "name": "Pendleton Woolen Mills"}, {"id": 51798, "name": "Gus* Modern"}, {"id": 47967, "name": "Republic of Fritz Hansen"}, {"id": 45516, "name": "Venini"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 53985, "name": "nanamica"}, {"id": 18521, "name": "This Is Ground"}, {"id": 53986, "name": "Paul McCobb"}, {"id": 53987, "name": "Matteo Thun"}, {"id": 53988, "name": "Spike Jonze"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 132, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181105214857gH4ZSfYUA3v08P9s.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Music Dopp Kit by This Is Ground</h3><p>关于洗漱用品、3C 用品的收纳包市面上已经很多了，它们都聚焦于解决人们在收纳时遇到的各种不方便情境。比如洛杉矶品牌 This Is Ground，就推出了各种皮革收纳包，引导人们以更有条理的收纳方式收纳随身物品。</p><p>最近，This Is Ground 推出了新款收纳解决方案 Music Dopp Kit，致力于为音乐爱好者提供收纳各种音乐配件装备的小包。Music Dopp Kit 的样式模仿了老式录音机的样式，复古且极具质感，整体采用优质皮革制成，配有各种皮带，拉链内部有隔层，以及将耳机牢牢固定在收纳包里的皮环，特别适合出差、旅行时携带。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215026OiGhpM2Er1R0lCz9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.185156\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215026iCv7NZfYLOghjnbz.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.791358\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215025V75bqmXYLPFcM83g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.758333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018110521502797IWPpdSmuXg42jB.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.818519\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215025pcFBHTWbALxfNiyh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源<a href=\"https://www.musicdoppkit.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">：Music Dopp Kit</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The North Face Purple Label x Spike Jonze</h3><p>户外品牌 The North Face 与东京知名户外品牌 nanamica 共同打造的日本专属支线 Purple Label，最近与美国导演 Spike Jonze 合作推出全新旅行袋系列。</p><p>整个系列包括 3-Way Bag 和 Shuttle Roller 两款，后者选用了大部分航空公司规定的手提行李尺寸，两款均采用了由意大利 PARA 社所生产的羊毛格子布材料制成，将户外产品的机能性与时髦感十足的格子纹融合起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215117PYfZGXq20J4gerys.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811052151174TieUujKX5nLaRMl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215117mRajKLt4PnCJ1h62.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215117Cnc1BTls9AERb35V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.nanamica.com/news/nanamica/8592/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nanamica</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Limited Edition Series of Opaque Vessels by Matteo Thun for Venini</h3><p>意大利建筑师 Matteo Thun 采用冷加工技术，为威尼斯穆拉诺岛的玻璃制造商 Venini 制作了一系列不透明的吹制玻璃花瓶。</p><p>花瓶是光滑的不透明表面，固定在 Santafiore 石材瓷砖上，目前正在米兰 Venini 精品店的一个名为Silence of the Colors 的展览中展出。</p><p>为了制作限量版产品，Matteo Thun 采用了与雕刻相同的冷加工技术，使得玻璃瓶身的表面颜色更加柔和。设计师试图通过这一组作品创造形状和色调之间的平衡，使基底的粗糙多孔表面与玻璃的光滑表面形成鲜明对比。</p><p>“我希望吹制玻璃的复杂性能够释放出一种古老的感觉，就像早期的 Novecento 的画作一样，” Matteo Thun 表示。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215210RfH0Be6vTQqiSpCO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215209iTUGjP16pCWoaqh0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215210GgBY1Va7K6zjluHf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811052152119fpaibDFGPXznIhx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498308\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215211n1uDjZqGs7AxHQ36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.matteothun.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Matteo Thun</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Planner Coffee Tables by Paul McCobb for Fritz Hansen</h3><p>Paul McCobb 是 20 世纪美国知名的工业设计师之一，其设计风格以简洁线条和极简主义样式而闻名。最近，丹麦百年品牌 Republic of Fritz Hansen 决定重新推出 Paul McCobb 于 1953 年设计的标志性作品 Planner 咖啡桌，是其 Planner Group 系列的一部分。这也是 Republic of Fritz Hansen 重启 Paul McCobb 经典原创设计的第一步。</p><p>Planner™ 咖啡桌采用厚度小于 2.54 厘米的大理石台面，配有简单的黑色钢底座，看上去如同大理石桌面浮动在底座上一般。Planner™ 咖啡桌提供圆形、矩形和方形三个桌面版本，以及多种纹理和色彩的选择。售价 1417 美元起，<a href=\"https://fritzhansen.com/en-us/designers/paul-mccobb\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215305TslyXBvfPxQYgujq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811052153054pxho6jKYdIBUSHM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215305uFnoC1cZm7SlEqVx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215305brhjkU1VIzqYimHc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215305P6dQwhcVARCoHBm8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215306MkaTC41XmVIBdnRU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215306apC0kj2bolvKgDAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>2nd Chair Collection by Gus* Modern x Pendleton Woolen Mills </h3><p>去年，多伦多设计品牌 Gus* Modern 与美国老牌织物制造商 Pendleton Woolen Mills 合作推出限量版躺椅。最近双方再度联手推出最新限量版系列，以 Gus* Modern 的 Elk Chair 为基础，加入两种不同的 Pendleton® 图案，赋予它们清新的外观调性。</p><p>较轻的天然灰色椅子采用 Canyonlands Desert 面料装饰，白色背景与柔和的中性色调的融合，而黑灰色椅子则采用单色图案的 Diamond River Tonal Charcoal 织物装饰。纺织品牌 Sunbrella 出品的织物，耐用性极佳，也更易于保养和清理。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215342Otvxz4Lu2h7BaRS0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215342G5eZQCHzTAYp7Wmh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215342FN5loah7DuKPCc1g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.134375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181105215342FUrLoysdkmtK17pb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811052153436IrOuxtC8AT2N3Hc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811052153436xhAMvblN0KP1eDE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://gusmodern.com/collections/gus-x-pendleton\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gus* Modern</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}